== 暗示手勢 ==
西方文化中，以手劃脖子暗示殺戮，是一種恐嚇性[[禁忌|禁忌]]手勢；嚴重程度更甚使人反感的手勢[[豎中指|比中指]]。2013年，球員凯文·杜兰特因賽中做出此一禁忌手勢，遭[[NBA|聯盟]]處以2萬5千美元罰款。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Durant fined $25,000 for 'menacing gesture'|url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/9165554/kevin-durant-oklahoma-city-thunder-fined-25000-nba-menacing-gesture|accessdate=2020-11-17|date=2013-04-12|work=ESPN.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317052036/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/9165554/kevin-durant-oklahoma-city-thunder-fined-25000-nba-menacing-gesture|dead-url=no}}</ref>

自2014年起，這死亡威脅手勢會令歐美人士厭惡並想到[[恐怖組織|恐怖組織]][[伊斯兰国|ISIS]]斬首行為。<ref>{{cite news|title=Refugee or terrorist? Shocking moment migrant makes ISIS-inspired beheading gesture|url=http://www.express.co.uk/news/world/607179/Refugee-terrorist-migrant-ISIS-inspired-beheading-gesture-watch|publisher=Daily Express|date=2015-09-22|author=OLI SMITH|accessdate=2018-09-29|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226155429/https://www.express.co.uk/news/world/607179/Refugee-terrorist-migrant-ISIS-inspired-beheading-gesture-watch|dead-url=no}}</ref>

